        "synopsis": {
            "value": "The story seeks to find an answer in the secretive relationships we hold in today’s society. Jeong Seon is a competent and successful career woman who works as a deputy manager at Sung Woon Department Store. Her job as a member of the VIP Management Team is to satisfy the top one percent of customers who are the special VIPs and VVIPs. Not only is she professional at work, but she has\n\na happy household with a wonderful husband, Seong Jun.\n\nHowever, one day she receives an anonymous text message. It says that her romantic husband is having an affair with someone at the office. Anxious to lose everything she has, she desperately studies the office and her co-workers to find out the woman Seong Jun is seeing. In the course of events, secrets behind each of the workers at the VIP Management Team are revealed. Will Jeong Seon find out the truth behind the anonymous text message?",
            "source": "asianwiki (Fallback: mydramalist)",
            "source_link": "https://mydramalist.com/33008-v-i-p"
        },
